name: Iced in Hoth, Stormtrooper
description:
Vintage Star Wars Hoth Storm trooper.

Note: I choose toys to paint that are past their prime (in paint/parts or shape). This toy has visible history and is not perfect. VINTAGE aka weak plastic and noticeable damage to original toy. New head glued on old toy.

I paint my canvas paintings in bright colours and played with painting on a new medium, these "toys". They are frankly just for fun and often called as experiments with colour. They are not perfect, they are just custom paints. Spray sealed but not good for food or outdoor use. Not for playing purposes, nor for children. Display and photo-bombing only.
